<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Sobre o Sistema (SSR)</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 40px; text-align: center; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: inline-block; min-width: 300px; }
        h1 { color: #007bff; }
        .stat { font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0; color: #555; }
        .number { font-weight: bold; color: #333; font-size: 22px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Sistema Escolar UniFAAT</h1>
        <p>Relatório gerado via <strong>Server-Side Rendering (EJS)</strong></p>
        <p>Data: <%= dataAtual %></p>
        
        <hr>
        
        <div class="stat">
            Usuários de Acesso: <span class="number"><%= totalUsers %></span>
        </div>

        <div class="stat">
            Professores Cadastrados: <span class="number"><%= totalProfessores %></span>
        </div>
        
        <br>
        <a href="http://localhost:5173" style="text-decoration: none; color: #007bff; font-weight: bold;">
            &larr; Voltar para o Sistema
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>